{"tid":1799719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整隻黑掉…加藤鷹60歲現況曝　名器「金手指」已破爛不堪","createTime":"2019-12-27T07:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T10:25:00.000Z","uid":53379,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"673e2dd531ad1c7696283bd20f5f5ee3975559d4","tid":1799719,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">整隻黑掉&hellip;加藤鷹60歲現況曝　名器「金手指」已破爛不堪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有「金手指」名號的日本前AV男優加藤鷹，雖然早已在2013年時就宣布退休，但至今為止他的人氣還是很高，除了常常受邀參加活動外，在媒體前的曝光度也相當高，聖誕節時他在社群媒體上分享自己的近況，但引以為傲的金手指卻以不復當年榮光，甚至還有「發黑」的情況，讓加藤鷹自己忍不住開玩笑說已經破爛不堪了。<br />\n<br />\n加藤鷹昔日以手技了得聞名於AV界，生涯與超過8000位女優交戰，拍攝超過15000部作品，一雙手讓許多對手「苦不堪言」，成為許多影迷心中的「天王」，2013年退休後「金手指」也成為絕響，不過他也開通社群媒體，持續與影迷分享自己的近況。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節時，加藤鷹就貼出一張手指的近況照，只見指甲部分顏色明顯黯淡發黑，看起來有點灰指甲的感覺，皮膚也有大片脫皮的痕跡，讓他自嘲「經過洗滌、金手指、破爛不堪」，網友也紛紛說「這是被腐蝕了呀」、「輝煌戰績下的產物」、「這算不算是工作傷害啊」、「中毒不淺呀大師！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/27/2325762-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F27%2F2325762-XXL.jpg&h=b986f8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲加藤鷹曝光「金手指」近況。（圖／翻攝自加藤鷹推特）<br />\n<br />\n「戰果輝煌」的加藤鷹，其實一開始根本沒想過要當男優，只是在片場擔任攝影助理，不過某次拍攝時男優不知為何沒出現，監督在沒有辦法的情況下只好麻煩加藤鷹協助拍攝，當時他還只答應幫忙拍3部片，想不到技術太好的他一舉成名，後續片約接連而至，希望他能正式出道成為男優，他才勉強點頭答應，最終成為「一代天王」。（黃朝郁報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=661408&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=IwAR1-eFGQYWfAjBb7Ya8ma52GU8iWNcwpBYRn3QG8iiGIrkeckHDqAKaY24E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D661408%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3DIwAR1-eFGQYWfAjBb7Ya8ma52GU8iWNcwpBYRn3QG8iiGIrkeckHDqAKaY24E&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHcg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=d188a80e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D661408%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3DIwAR1-eFGQYWfAjBb7Ya8ma52GU8iWNcwpBYRn3QG8iiGIrkeckHDqAKaY24E&h=95039f81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=661408&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=IwAR1-eFGQYWfAjBb7Ya8ma52GU8iWNcwpBYRn3QG8iiGIrkeckHDqAKaY24E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻手指會咁架咩"},{"pid":"381b98fd4b0b0de3523bf9ecf927c544c0a1a394","tid":1799719,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b4352fa318fddfbebc1ee4e6829be060878fe9","tid":1799719,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"Po時事台做乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"2e2298c73dd43aec38077ea4912182006886fa12","tid":1799719,"uid":177213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"Pr公司又放鹹嘢阻住啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9bee82c4d333e65283eb4d3b6c0b5a89d0fc28","tid":1799719,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"5毛露底"},{"pid":"76be06da9d23055c4c3f84a6f68a1e4e13687014","tid":1799719,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"Pr公司又放鹹嘢阻住啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254e82077cbd62ab596b7f3084813e399ef9ee3c","tid":1799719,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:22:59